data.message: Thanks for the sponsor for the delicious Lao food and birthday cake, everyone brings home three TCM acupuncture points for self healing!

Feedback, something to take away with you : Hi Wendy,

This is Russell. The energy strategist.

I have learnt a lot more about the healthiness after the talk. 

To be healthy, it is very important that a person must be able to self massage. He or she can learn methods of doing massage for him/herself.

Everyday self massage your own body is very important.

2nd thing - everyday must have good water to drink.

3rd thing - nutricious food and drink will keep detox and rejuvenate your body cells.

Thanks.

This session's topic is all about "Weight", what you put into your mouth and how the Qi in your body works.

The balance of Qi & Blood is very important for body weight.
The fatty person requires to nourish Qi, and the skinny person requires to enrich blood, According to the theory of Traditional Chinese Medicine .This is the reason that to lose or increase weight is very difficult.
氣血的平衡對人體體重的影響非常重要. 根據傳統中醫的理論: 胖補氣,瘦補血. 氣血失衡是胖子瘦不了,瘦子胖不了的原因.
